markup=pango  # ‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö pango markup ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏°‡∏µ icon ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏™‡∏µ HTML ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ



######################################
# Greeting Block (‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠ user)
[greetings]
label=
command=echo "$USER"
color=#f5af19
interval=once

######################################
# Time / Date Block
[time]
label=üïí
command=~/.config/i3blocks/scripts/time.sh
interval=1
signal=10
color=#61afef

######################################
# CPU Usage Block
[cpu]
label=üíª
command=awk '{u=$2+$4; t=$2+$4+$5} NR==1{cpu=u; total=t} NR==2{print int((u-cpu)/(t-total)*100)"%"}' <(grep 'cpu ' /proc/stat; sleep 1; grep 'cpu ' /proc/stat)
interval=5
color=#98c379

######################################
# Memory Usage Block
[memory]
label=üß†
command=free -h | awk '/Mem:/ { print $3 "/16G "  }'
interval=10
color=#c678dd

######################################
[battery]
label= 
command=~/.config/i3blocks/battery.sh
interval=1
signal=10   
command=~/.config/i3blocks/scripts/battery.sh
color=#61afef
